Usage: create_physical_partitions [-help] {{<partition_spec> | -logical_spec <spec>} [-group_instance_suffix <string>] [-check_only ] [[-undo  [-pre_full_upf <string> [-incremental_block_upfs <string>]]]]}

-help                               # Prints out the command usage
<partition_spec>                    # Specification in a format of {
                                    # [common_parent_hinst:]<h_cell_name1>
                                    # {<boxes list1>}
                                    # [common_parent_hinst:]<h_cell_name2>
                                    # {<boxes list2>} ...} (string, optional)
-check_only                         # Check constraints consistency for
                                    # create_physical_partition (bool, optional)
-group_instance_suffix <string>     # group instance suffix, default is i
                                    # (string, optional)
-incremental_block_upfs <string>    # incremental block upfs (string, optional)
-logical_spec <spec>                # Specification in a format of {
                                    # <h_cell_name1> {<hinst_or_inst list1>}
                                    # <h_cell_name2> {<hinst_or_inst list2>}
                                    # ...} (string, optional)
-pre_full_upf <string>              # -pre_full_upf is mandatory when -undo set
                                    # in MSV design (string, optional)
-undo                               # Undo physical group, -pre_full_upf is
                                    # mandatory when -undo set in MSV design.
                                    # (bool, optional)